|----------|-------|-----------|
| 🔴 Critical | 2 | Triple-regex chain in `Underscore` (4 allocs/call); per-match allocs in `Pascalize` (~5 allocs/match) |
| 🟡 Moderate | 3 | `Camelize` substring; inconsistent `Compiled` vs `GeneratedRegex`; per-instance `Compiled` in `InflectionRule` |
| ℹ️ Info | 1 | Unsealed `InflectionRule` class |

